<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>RoamingRoof - Discover Your Next Home</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      /* Updated color palette to match your site's theme */
      --primary: #1F2937; /* Dark Charcoal */
      --primary-dark: #111827;
      --dark: #1F2937;
      --light: #f9fafb;
      --grey: #6B7280;
      --border-color: #E5E7EB;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--light);
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    /* --- Header --- */
    header {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      padding: 1.5rem 5%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .brand {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .auth-buttons button {
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border: 1px solid white;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-login {
        background: transparent;
        color: white;
    }
    .btn-login:hover {
        background: white;
        color: var(--dark);
    }
    .btn-signup {
        background: white;
        color: var(--dark);
    }
    .btn-signup:hover {
        background: #f0f0f0;
        border-color: #f0f0f0;
    }

    /* --- Hero Section --- */
    .hero {
      height: 90vh;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580587771525-78b9dba3b914?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    /* --- Hero Search Form --- */
    .search-form-hero {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 50px;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .search-input {
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      flex-grow: 1;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    .search-input::placeholder {
        color: var(--grey);
    }
    .search-button-hero {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .search-button-hero:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
    }
    .search-button-hero i {
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* --- Features Section --- */
    .features {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      background-color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .section-subheading {
        color: var(--grey);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .features-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--light);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      flex: 1 1 280px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .feature-card .icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--primary); /* Use dark charcoal for icons */
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--grey);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* --- Footer --- */
    footer {
      background: #F3F4F6;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6B7280;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }
    .footer-brand {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--dark);
    }

    /* --- Media Queries --- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      .search-form-hero {
        flex-direction: column;
        border-radius: 20px;
        gap: 1rem;
        background: transparent;
        box-shadow: none;
      }
      .search-input {
          border-radius: 50px;
          text-align: center;
          padding: 1rem;
      }
      header {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="brand">RoamingRoof</div>
    <div class="auth-buttons">
      <button class="btn-login" onclick="location.href='/login'">Login</button>
      <button class="btn-signup" onclick="location.href='/signup'">Sign Up</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Find Your Next Home, Anywhere</h1>
      <p>The perfect space is waiting for you. Discover curated homes for every journey and budget.</p>
      
      <form class="search-form-hero" action="/listings" method="GET">
        <input name="q" class="search-input" type="text" placeholder="Search destinations (e.g., Mumbai)" />
        <button class="search-button-hero" type="submit">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>Search
        </button>
      </form>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Why Choose RoamingRoof?</h2>
    <p class="section-subheading">We provide a seamless and secure experience, so you can focus on settling in, not stressing out.</p>
    <div class="features-list">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
        <h3>Trusted & Verified</h3>
        <p>Every property is manually screened for quality and safety, ensuring a worry-free stay.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i></div>
        <h3>For Every Budget</h3>
        <p>From cozy city apartments to luxurious villas in serene locations, find a space that fits your needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i></div>
        <h3>Transparent Pricing</h3>
        <p>No hidden fees or surprise charges. The price you see is the price you pay, every time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 <span class="footer-brand">RoamingRoof</span>. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
